<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.11">
<l>kaṇṇaik kuḷirak kalanteṅkum nōkkik</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṭikamaḻ pūṅkuḻa lārka</l>
<l>ḷeṇṇattu ḷeṉṟu miruntutit tikkum</l>
<l rend="indent">perumāṉē yeṅka ḷamutē</l>
<l>yuṇṇak kaṉikaḷ taruvaṉ kaṭippoṉṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">nōvāmē kātuk kiṭuvaṉ</l>
<l>paṇṇaik kiḻiyac cakaṭa mutaittiṭṭa</l>
<l rend="indent">paṟpanā pāviṅkē vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Mingling [with women] in order to please the eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">looking everywhere,</l>
<l>O sweet Lord, always in the thoughts of ladies</l>
<l rend="indent">with curls with fragrant blossoms,</l>
<l>O Our Nectar, I will give [you] ripe fruits to eat,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] put just one earring in your ear without pain.</l>
<l>O Padmanābha who kicked the cart so that the bamboo was destroyed!</l>
<l rend="indent">Come here!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
